data.title: Centre List of Exam 2020
data.meta_description: centre_list_of_exam_2020 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is a list of examination centers for the Madhyamik Shiksha Parishad, Uttar Pradesh board exams in 2020. It includes 131 centers across Agra district listed by their type (A, B, or C), center name, and location. The centers include both government schools and private institutions.
